        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Sober Home Fraud Detection Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to publish common indicators of potentially fraudulent or disreputable recovery housing (alcohol- and drug-free shared living environments that promote recovery from substance use disorders), such as with respect to unusual billing practices, longer than average occupancies, and excessive levels of drug testing.</p>]]></text>
